26
00:04:37.942 --> 00:04:42.377
In the event of death. I hereby
direct that my body be cremated.

27
00:04:42.779 --> 00:04:45.912
<i>and that my ashes be
scattered on Mount Everest.</i>

28
00:04:46.014 --> 00:04:49.486
