our sacred water again.

68
00:10:46.942 --> 00:10:48.845
Vijay. where have you been?

69
00:10:49.214 --> 00:10:52.948
-Take this in. Listen to this! Hear this.
-Grandfather is dead.

70
00:10:54.982 --> 00:10:56.747
