-Shit.
-<i> ...AB304 to Kathmandu</i>

86
00:12:18.332 --> 00:12:20.772
-<i> is now boarding for departure.</i>
-Sorry. bro.

87
00:12:35.684 --> 00:12:37.319
<i>Hey. hey.</i>

88
00:12:37.421 --> 00:12:38.554
